verbose_text: While all SIRPalpha + cDCs comprise IRF4 + IRF8 - bona fide cDC2 in mouse, two populations of SIRPalpha + cDCs have been detected in humans : a population of bona fide cDC2 with a CD1c + IRF4 + IRF8 - phenotype and a population of CD1c - cDCs showing the typical IRF4 int IRF8 int expression observed in the monocyte-macrophage population.
